    Closeable, DatasetGraph

    public class DatasetGraphMaker
extends DatasetGraphMap
    Implementation of a DatasetGraph as an open set of graphs where all graphs "exist". New graphs are created (via the policy of a GraphMaker) when a getGraph call is made to a graph that has not been allocated.
